 {frame}  
   {Programming Languages}  
 {itemize}  
  <1-> \Sn{programming} \hateq writing  
\sns{program?program}\lec{Telling the \sn{computer} what to do}  
  <2->  
 {sassertion}[style=remark]  
The \sn{computer} does exactly as told

{itemize}  
