   a \definame[post=s]{code block} surrounded with \texttt{<\char37} and  
\texttt{\char37 >}, and  
   an \definame[post=s]{stpl-files?expression} \lstinline[mathescape]|{{$\pmetavar{exp}$}}| as long  
as $\pmetavar{exp}$ evaluates to a string.  
    {itemize}  
